item.description: This is our biggest fundraiser of the year! Come out to dance (cover will be about $10-15, with part of the proceeds going to our group), bring your friends, advertise EVERYWHERE, and help find cool donations for raffle prizes from local businesses that you frequent. No dancing talent or experience required. No partner required either! Contact: Kaitlyn at internationalservice@bostonrotaract.org

group.name: Boston Rotaract - A Service/Social Club for 18-30 Yr Olds
